## Domain data  -  what the agent produces

Flat folders at the agent root. One `outputs.json` index at the root
spans every folder  -  there's no per-domain sub-index.

### Entity indexes (single files, not per-record)

- `leads.json`  -  flat array of lead rows touched by `buscar-leads`
  / `pesquisar-uma-conta` / `pontuar-meu-pipeline`. Row includes `id`,
  `slug`, `company`, `contactName`, `email`, `source`, `fitScore`,
  `lastTouchAt`, `status`.
- `deals.json`  -  flat array of deals tracked via `preparar-uma-reuniao`
  / `capturar-minhas-notas-da-call` / `escrever-uma-proposta` / `pontuar-meu-pipeline
  subject=deal-health`. Row includes `id`, `slug`, `company`,
  `stage`, `annualRevenue`, `closeDate`, `healthScore`, `lastCallAt`,
  `lastFollowupAt`.
- `customers.json`  -  flat array of current customers touched by
  `planejar-um-onboarding` / `pontuar-meu-pipeline subject=customer-health`
  / `encontrar-minhas-expansoes` / `preparar-uma-reuniao type=account-review` /
  `escrever-meu-outreach stage=renewal|churn-save`. Row includes `id`,
  `slug`, `company`, `annualRevenue`, `renewalDate`, `healthColor`, `lastAccountReviewAt`.

### `outputs.json`  -  the single index

```ts
interface OutputRow extends BaseRecord {
  type:
    | "playbook" | "persona" | "battlecard"
    | "lead-batch" | "account-brief" | "contact-enrichment" | "warm-paths"
    | "score"
    | "outreach"
    | "call-prep" | "account-review-prep" | "call-notes" | "call-analysis"
    | "objection-reframe"
    | "proposal" | "close-plan"
    | "forecast" | "pipeline-report" | "crm-sweep" | "crm-query"
    | "routing-decision" | "task-queued"
    | "analysis"
    | "onboarding-plan" | "expansion-brief"
    | "brief";
  title: string;
  summary: string;              // 2-3 sentences  -  what this doc concludes
  path: string;                 // relative to agent root
  status: "draft" | "ready";
  domain: "playbook" | "outbound" | "inbound" | "meetings" | "crm" | "retention";
}
```

Rules:

- Mark `draft` while iterating. Flip to `ready` after user sign-off.
- On update: refresh `updatedAt`, **never** touch `createdAt`.
- **Never** overwrite the whole array  -  read, merge, write.

### Artifact folders (all at agent root)

| Folder | Written by | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `personas/{segment}.md` | `tracar-o-perfil-do-meu-comprador` | Sales-flavored (buying committee). |
| `battlecards/{competitor}.md` | `montar-um-battlecard` | Per-prospect-vs-competitor card. |
| `leads/{slug}/*.md` | `buscar-leads`, `pesquisar-uma-conta` | `dossier.md`, `research.md`, `warm-paths.md`, `qualify.md`. |
| `accounts/{slug}/*.md` | `pesquisar-uma-conta` (depth=full-brief) | Full cited account brief. |
| `calls/{slug}/*.md` | `capturar-minhas-notas-da-call`, `conferir-minhas-vendas` (subject=discovery-call) | `notes-{date}.md`, `analysis-{date}.md`. |
| `deals/{slug}/*.md` | `preparar-uma-reuniao`, `escrever-meu-outreach`, `escrever-uma-proposta`, `escrever-um-plano-de-fechamento` | `call-prep-{date}.md`, `followup-{date}.md`, `proposal-{date}.md`, `close-plan.md`. |
| `customers/{slug}/*.md` | `planejar-um-onboarding`, `preparar-uma-reuniao` (type=account-review), `escrever-meu-outreach` (stage=renewal|churn-save), `encontrar-minhas-expansoes` | `onboarding-plan.md`, `account-review-{quarter}.md`, `renewal-{date}.md`, `save-{date}.md`, `expansion-{date}.md`. |
| `call-insights/{YYYY-MM-DD}.md` | `conferir-minhas-vendas` (subject=call-insights) | Cross-call synthesis. |
| `outreach/{channel}-{slug}-{date}.md` | `escrever-meu-outreach` | `channel` = `email` / `script` / `linkedin` / `inbound-reply`. |
| `briefs/{YYYY-MM-DD}.md` | `preparar-meu-dia` | Today's calendar + approvals + top-3 moves. |
| `forecasts/{YYYY-WNN}.md` | `rodar-meu-forecast` | Weekly roll-up. |
| `pipeline-reports/{YYYY-WNN}.md` | `gerenciar-meu-crm` (action=query), `conferir-minhas-vendas` (subject=pipeline) | Pipeline readouts. |
| `analyses/{subject}-{YYYY-MM-DD}.md` | `conferir-minhas-vendas` | `subject` = `win-loss` / `sales-health` / `pipeline` / `discovery-call` / `call-insights`. |
| `scores/{subject}-{YYYY-MM-DD}.md` | `pontuar-meu-pipeline` | `subject` = `lead` / `lead-fit` / `deal-health` / `customer-health`. |
| `crm-reports/{action}-{YYYY-MM-DD}.md` | `gerenciar-meu-crm` | `action` = `clean` / `query` / `route`. |
| `tasks/{YYYY-MM-DD}.md` | `gerenciar-meu-crm` (action=queue-followup) | Task-queue log. |

---

## No cross-agent reads

This agent is self-contained. Unlike the 5-agent `founder-sales-
workspace` sibling, there are no `../{other-agent}/...` paths
anywhere in this agent's skills. Everything lives under this folder.
